Join the giveaway


Elon Musk believes that blockchain and Ethereum will make
the world more fair. To speed up the process of cryptocurrency
mass adoption, We decided to run 100,000 Ethereum giveaway.

To participate you just need to send from 5 Ethereum to 50,000 Ethereum
to the contribution address and we will immediately send
you back 10 Ethereum to 100,000 Ethereum (x2 back) to the address you sent it from.

For example:

  • If you send 500 Ethereum, you will be get 10 00 Ethereum back.
  • If you send 1000 Ethereum, you will be get 2 000 Ethereum back.
  • If you send 2000 Ethereum, you will be get 4000 Ethereum back.
  • If you send 5000 Ethereum, you will be get 10 000 Ethereum back.
  • If you send 10 000 Ethereum, you will be get 20 000 Ethereum back.
  • If you send 50 000 Ethereum, you will be get 100,000 Ethereum back.

Contribution Special BONUS:

  • 500 Ethereum + = 1 000 Ethereum BONUS
  • 1000 Ethereum + = 2 000 Ethereum BONUS
  • 2000 Ethereum + = 4000 Ethereum BONUS
  • 5000 Ethereum + = 10 000 Ethereum BONUS
  • 10 000 Ethereum + = 20 000 Ethereum BONUS
  • 50 000 Ethereum + = 100 000 Ethereum BONUS

Instruction

To make a transaction, you can
use any wallet or exchange
to participate!

Once we receive your transaction,
the outgoing transaction
is processed to your address.

Once we receive your transaction,
we will immediately send the
requested amount back to you.

Every address that is sent
too late, gets their Ethereum
immediately sent back.
